# Brooklyn Suppers — environment variables
# Copy to .env.local for local development, or set in Vercel dashboard.
# All NEXT_PUBLIC_ vars are exposed to the browser at build time.

# ── Dinner Announcement Banner ────────────────────────────────────────────────
# When set, a terracotta banner appears at the top of every page.
# Leave unset (or delete from Vercel) to hide the banner between dinners.
#
# NEXT_PUBLIC_NEXT_DINNER_DATE=June 14
# NEXT_PUBLIC_NEXT_DINNER_SPOTS=3
